{"tid":735012,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【撼贏無綫】ViuTV直播  138萬觀眾睇住英格蘭入四強","createTime":"2018-07-09T06:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T07:53:08.000Z","uid":62257,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"61d71e2b5b5c99edf5df2f721250f7040ebe323e","tid":735012,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:49:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180709/58419209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180709%2F58419209&d=o3r6j3M7AqXltrNppPm1YfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=2ba69a64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180709%2F58419209&h=2c96b357\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180709/58419209</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180709/large/1531109020_fe3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180709%2Flarge%2F1531109020_fe3e.jpg&h=98c00035&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英格蘭前晚喺俄羅斯世界盃半準決賽以2:0贏咗瑞典，成功躋身4強，今次亦係英格蘭28年來首次踢入世盃準決賽。<br />\n<br />\n英格蘭一向受港人熱捧，免費電視ViuTV前晚10點直播英格蘭對瑞典呢場重要賽事，當然受到全港球迷關心，據了解，呢場賽事平均收18點，有118萬人次，最高係21點，有138萬人次，比上次ViuTV直播英格蘭狂炒巴拿馬嗰場分組賽成績重好。<br />\n至於無綫方面，據了解星期六晚9點半至10點半播《美女廚房》平均12點（79萬人次），跌咗5點、10點半至11點《3日2夜》平均6點（39萬人次），跌咗7點、11點至11點半《勁歌金曲》平均3點（20萬人次），跌咗4點，而11點半至11點45分播《晚間新間》平均只有2點（13萬人次），跌咗5點。<br />\n<br />\n至於法國以2:0淘汰烏拉圭嘅8強賽事，平均17點（111萬人次），最高19點（125萬人次），收視成績都好理想。"},{"pid":"83f4f5faa7fc00b656282bc9582c9b5032cf6878","tid":735012,"uid":62257,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:53:23.000Z","msg":"砌贏美女廚房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199079e162db327f487b79d72c454288537ef46b","tid":735012,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:53:53.000Z","msg":"打多陣飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db3b4cd1b9d0f671a1be3f85224e66edeb698877","tid":735012,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266fae67442dcda064e4b68b70ac2451354ffd45","tid":735012,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:08:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3bba0298ed76a79c70eae56b883e15978a015a2","tid":735012,"uid":31354,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"今晚東張閪望又可以對住個收視打飛機<br />\n<br />\n唔知又衝破幾多萬億收視"},{"pid":"dbeccdce13863949f76279ce63ba325c933b8506","tid":735012,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"266fae67442dcda064e4b68b70ac2451354ffd45","tid":735012,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:08:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272e19fba928816145c17dddff732f7fe636ac2d","tid":735012,"uid":124537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3bba0298ed76a79c70eae56b883e15978a015a2","tid":735012,"uid":31354,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"今晚東張閪望又可以對住個收視打飛機<br />\n<br />\n唔知又衝破幾多萬億收視"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:53:08.000Z","msg":"精蟲萬億就有佢份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}